==Instructions==

In the arrange window double-click the audio file you want to reverse.
The sample editor window should open up.
In the sample editor window go to the functions menu and then choose Reverse.
 
If the Reverse option is grayed out try making a copy of the audio file (bounce in place) and then reverse the copy.



